= SSH demonstrations =

This page provides examples how SSH commands can be executed from the fluidOps platform. This page applies the examples as presented on [[Help:SDK-Workflows]]:

<source>
{{#widget: CodeExecution | 
 passContext = false
 | userInput = {{ 
      {{ name = 'host'
       | componentType = 'SIMPLE'
      }} | 
      {{ name = 'user'
       | componentType = 'SIMPLE'
      }} | 
      {{ name = 'password'
       | componentType = 'PASSWORD'
      }} | 
      {{ name = 'command'
       | componentType = 'TEXTAREA'
      }} }}
 | args = {{ '%host' | '%user' | '%password' | '%command' }}
 | method = 'exec'
 | label = 'Run SSH'
 | clazz = 'ssh.SSHConnect'
}}
</source>

